<h2>About Us</h2>
<p>
Our club was founded in Spring of 2013. 
The purpose of the Running Club is to bring together WPI students who are interested in running and provide an environment which supports personal growth and camaraderie. We create a social and constructive atmosphere with regular practices and meetings.
</p>

<h3>Mailing List</h3>
The mailing list is a low traffic way of staying notified about weekly running plans. 

Please email the officers at <a href="mailto:running-execs@wpi.edu">running-execs@wpi.edu</a> to be added to the list.


<h3>Officers</h3>
<ul>
    <li><b>President:     </b><a href="mailto:jwcolfer@wpi.edu"> Jack Colfer</a></li>
    <li><b>Vice President:</b><a href="mailto:sclaudage@wpi.edu"> Steve Laudage</a></li>
    <li><b>Secretary:     </b><a href="mailto:bgsarkis@wpi.edu"> Ben Sarkis</a></li>
    <li><b>Treasurer:     </b><a href="mailto:imdiamond@wpi.edu"> Ian Diamond</a></li>
    <li><b>Team Captain:  </b><a href="mailto:eszandrow@wpi.edu"> Eric Zandrow</a></li>
</ul>

<h3>Constitution</h3>
You can find a PDF of our constitution <a href="http://run.wpi.edu/pdf/constitution.pdf">here</a>.

<h3>Local Running Clubs</h3>
We are not affiliated with any of these groups, but they have a similar mission to ours.
